        "description": "<p>Prevents loopback request errors in WordPress environments using Docker such as wp-env.</p>\n<p>Replace requests to localhost with host.docker.internal, and if https, change to http and turn off sslverify.</p>\n<p>There are no settings. Just enable this plugin.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload the <code>localhost2host-docker-internal</code> folder to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the <code>Plugins</code> menu in WordPress</li>\n</ol>\n"
    },
